title: Rein Music
description:
**Rein Music** is a free music bot that prioritizes **Quality** for the streaming experience on every voice channel.

**Prefix Usage:**
`r!play (URL)` or `(Music Title)`, `r!join` or `r!join (URL) / (Music Title)`, `r!leave`, `r!autoplay`.

The application is still under development. For bug reporting or suggestions contact <@&1374411351660957818> if in the **Kirashore** Discord Server
